{"tid":630270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"電視財演討論","createTime":"2018-04-15T12:50:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T14:21:54.000Z","uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ea90b1b1350241b181415b7b5852aa746a2092","tid":630270,"uid":141263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:50:15.000Z","msg":"有睇開財經節目 覺得電視個班教散戶d操作好求其<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而施凌係youtube仲認真少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可以逐個討論下，我先 郭sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n波幅理論幾好 不過上年中同今年頭都打破左某d定律 <br />\n長期大好友 用恒指成份股比重黎分析大市<br />\n<br />\n不過成日叫人買中人壽 最近個次係年頭叫人買 話其他股升晒 得中人壽未升 而且睇好a股 總之a股一升 2628就會大升。而且因為2628冇升過 所以跌都唔會跌得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果a股大跌 而且2628跌得勁過升左好多嘅平保<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然 佢都經常叫人買939 700 2318個d，都係走勢好嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人講下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我夜d再講多個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb87dd1a0c09453fae0f4ccb40eed196f675b28","tid":630270,"uid":84771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"施凌拆左伙<br />\n施好似數浪冇凌咁勁<br />\n拆左伙之後，施成日請d 19 樓市財演叫人買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外，如果唔計566呢人生污點，林一嗚睇大方向應該幾準。黃國英有時我會睇下，不過有點硬好，成日笑沈大師，但亦因爲咁而唔敢睇淡"},{"pid":"8db8751a2c408eb4debb60ef9aa674cc8b68a3bc","tid":630270,"uid":108814,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"賊略王<br />\n專推老千股 仙股<br />\n幫莊出貨"},{"pid":"53880c6a88b34a17f2eecc1301294621985ef15e","tid":630270,"uid":33263,"like":1,"di